cc:Work.dc:title: Chinese symbol on red scroll remix
cc:Work.dc:description: I attempted a remix of this scroll uploaded by rejon. I tried to clean it up a bit but still keep the patchwork look of it. Added a frame and a shadow also. By the way, thats the 'f' character and it means LUCK, GOOD FORTUNE or something like that. (The original upload requested a translation too.)
